The "SocialAlerts Discord Bot" is a versatile and user-friendly Discord bot designed to keep users informed and engaged with their favorite social media platforms. This extension allows Discord server members to subscribe to and receive notifications about activity on various social networks, including Instagram, Twitch, Reddit, and YouTube, among others.
When you navigate on your browser. Free6 detect a link to a social network for you, it triggers the extension and you can then configure to receive alert on you Discord server for a specific content.
